highlights.text: “Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 128 weeks straight.
“You Need To Calm Down” by Taylor Swift is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #4.
Billie Eilish has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “bad guy” is the highest at #2.
“Te Soñé de Nuevo” by Ozuna is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 45 spots at #139.
